node.text:
30gs on AMC. Let the games begin!

I saw a lot of you request I do it, so fuck it let's have some fun.

Few reasons why this is a dumb AF move:

1. It's probably the most overvalued stock in history lol.  It was overvalued when I had it at $4.00 lol. 

2. Movie theaters got absolutely crushed during the pandemic.

3. This company is in a wild amount of debt.

4. Their future earnings look weak considering now major movies you can stream on opening day and that's how they put butts in seats. 

But having said all that remember, in this experiment I'm looking to "get rich over night".

So I'm betting on pure hype, speculation, and my fellow gamers on Reddit to take this shit 

"To The Moon".

Which ironically seems like the new way to play the market and get rich.

Example: Crypto.

Anyways, wish me luck y'all I'll let you know when I sell. Then I'll take all of that and bet it on something else.

Geneius > Genius.

node.text:
A decade ago I was checking in people at 24 hour Fitness for $8.00 an hour.

A decade ago I lived at my boys mom's house rent free but not guilt free. 

A decade ago I had a 400 credit score and 2 different banks send me to collections for overdraft fees. 

A decade ago temporarily defeated me but that shit didn't define me. 

You're the author of your life. Whatever happens next is what you decide to write.

Never forget that. 🙏🏿

Could have invested into crypto.

Could have bought penny stocks. 

Could have saved for a rainy day. 

My aunt could have had balls but then she'd be my uncle.

So I guess what I'm trying to say is...

1. Getting the city to shut down my street

And 

2. Paying a company to crane my new spa to my balcony was worth every fucking penny. 

Because I got the most underrated ROI of all-time:

Happiness! 

Cheers,  it's always impossible until somebody does it.

node.text:
"Well Warren Buffett still drives a beat up Chrysler".

Yah, fuck that noise. Happy 33rd birthday to me.

Got another lambo. Moved to the beach. Renewed our suite at the Padres.  Traveling. Speaking. Filming. Kicking it with my girls. 

Ads have now been seen 1,000,000,000 times. 

Day 60 of 75 hard, feeling like a fucking savage. 

Your boy is back. You know the vibes. Link in bio. Buy my shit. 

We just getting started.
